cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision techniques for recognizing indoor environments under simulated prosthetic vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and graphics (cs.GR) as it uses deep learning techniques to extract structural and object information from the scene.
